org.apache.calcite.adapter.enumerable

Class CodeGenerationBenchmark

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.calcite.adapter.enumerable.CodeGenerationBenchmark
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CodeGenerationBenchmark_jmhType_B1

    public class CodeGenerationBenchmark
extends Object
    A benchmark of the main methods that are dynamically generating and compiling Java code at runtime.

    The benchmark examines the behavior of existing methods and evaluates the potential of adding a caching layer on top.
